-- Personality: Madoquar is wise and motherly, though she still enjoys the
-- feeling of being a women despite being so old. At this age simple things
-- make her happy, like a nice berry wine and an apple. She lives by herself,
-- but is sometimes visited by adventurers. Every few hundred or years or so
-- she goes on a tour around the world to meet old people and new.

-- Background:  One of if not the oldest elves alive. She is famed for her
-- wisdom gained from being a live so long. Anyone who ever has the grace of
-- meeting her offers Madoquar a meal and night stay. Madoquar is loved by
-- all. She is characterized by an eye patch on her right eye that she got
-- when her village flooded when she was a small child. Or that's what she
-- wants people to think. In truth Quantisha Bakabrobaxt killed Madoquar 400
-- years go and took over her life. No one knows, no one who would TRULY know
-- The original essence of Madoquar are alive now.

-- Goals:
-- To live a happy and famous, but peaceful life.
-- Methods:
-- She does not really have to do anything. People come to her and give her
-- stuff and attention.
-- Goal: To make everyone believe she is Madoquar
-- Method: impeccable acting skills + charismatic smile + elven magic +
-- destroying all evidence.

